@startuml care-services-sync-example

skinparam roundcorner 20
skinparam defaultFontName Arial 
hide footbox

!pragma teoz true

participant  UC as "Update Client"
participant  QC as "Query Client"
participant  LRZa as "LRZa\nDirectory"
participant  QD as "Local Replica\n(Query Directory)"

activate UC
activate QC
note over QC: Initial load of local replica

QC -> LRZa: GET /Organization
activate LRZa
LRZa -> QC: Bundle (searchset)
QC -> LRZa: GET /Location
LRZa -> QC: Bundle (searchset)
QC -> LRZa: GET /HealthcareService
LRZa -> QC: Bundle (searchset)
QC -> LRZa: GET /Endpoint
LRZa -> QC: Bundle (searchset)
QC -> LRZa: GET /Device
LRZa -> QC: Bundle (searchset)
QC -> LRZa: GET /OrganizationAffiliation
LRZa -> QC: Bundle (searchset)
deactivate LRZa

QC -> QD: POST / (transaction bundle)\ninitial population
activate QD
QD -> QC: 200 OK
deactivate QD
deactivate QC

note over UC: Periodic incremental sync\n(e.g., every day)

UC -> LRZa: GET /Organization/_history?_since=2025-02-07T13:28:17
activate LRZa
LRZa -> UC: Bundle (history)
UC -> LRZa: GET /Location/_history?_since=2025-02-07T13:28:17
LRZa -> UC: Bundle (history)
UC -> LRZa: GET /HealthcareService/_history?_since=2025-02-07T13:28:17
LRZa -> UC: Bundle (history)
UC -> LRZa: GET /Endpoint/_history?_since=2025-02-07T13:28:17
LRZa -> UC: Bundle (history)
UC -> LRZa: GET /Device/_history?_since=2025-02-07T13:28:17
LRZa -> UC: Bundle (history)
UC -> LRZa: GET /OrganizationAffiliation/_history?_since=2025-02-07T13:28:17
LRZa -> UC: Bundle (history)
deactivate LRZa

note over UC: Consolidate and validate updates

UC -> QD: POST / (transaction bundle)\napply updates to replica
activate QD
QD -> UC: 200 OK
deactivate QD

note over UC,QD: Sync complete.\nPersist new watermark timestamp.
deactivate UC

@enduml
